These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, police-officer, videographer, scientist
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the videographer##1
2. the fisherman is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the scientist is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Job   | fisherman | police-officer | scientist | videographer |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, juice, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice | almond-milk  | sprite  | lemonade |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, volleyball, biathlon
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Sport   | volleyball        | biathlon     | climbing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, pony, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet         | rabbit | hamster | goldfish | pony |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, coach, photographer, lawyer
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the coach is the fan of punk##1
3. the photographer is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the engineer is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Job   | engineer | lawyer | photographer | coach |

