.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
City: prague, london, hannover, marseilles
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, japanese, malaysian
1. the italian is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the italian##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| City   | hannover      | london | marseilles | prague |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian     | indonesian  | japanese  |

