.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip, bellflower, dahlia
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person driving the ship is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | dahlia | bellflower | tulip    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

