.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, project-manager, teacher
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, poker, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the teacher is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the coach is between the teacher and the pilot##2
6. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the coach and the person playing poker##2
8. the coach is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | pilot | coach      | teacher | project-manager |
| Game   | bridge  | monopoly | mah-jongg    | poker            |

