.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, reggae, techno, jazz
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of reggae and the person eating pepper##2
4. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Music-Genre    | jazz     | reggae | r&b     | techno  |

