.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, card-games, collecting, skydiving
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games | skydiving        | sudoku    |

