.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, water
City: london, hamburg, nizza, prague
1. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta   | water   | juice      | tea      |
| City      | hamburg | nizza | prague | london |

