.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, badminton, cycling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, hip-hop, soul
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the fan of disco and the fan of hip-hop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport          | cycling | lacrosse  | badminton  | baseball |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | hip-hop | ambient | disco   |

