.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, water-polo, skateboarding, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Sport   | water-polo | sailing | skateboarding | swimming  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike  | train  | motorbike |

