.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero, western
4 different games are played: domino, whist, canasta, poker
1. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | family | martial-arts |
| Game           | poker     | domino     | canasta   | whist         |

