.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, spanish, egyptian, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the indonesian is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the spanish##2
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the spanish is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Nationality   | australian | spanish         | indonesian   | egyptian |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

