.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, gardening, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, sailing, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
5. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is sailing##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | gardening | board-games | chess    |
| Sport   | sailing | cycling  | basketball     | tennis |

