1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Pet     | goldfish      | hedgehog       | goat | fish     |

